n\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different line\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"the winner\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just made a mistake on the lay line,\\\" added Wilson, referring to the calculation required to reach the next mark, or buoy, in the quickest time.\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2770, \"end\": 2776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"score\": 0.9999185770356357, \"rank\": 8.010564304056107e-05, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"the lay line\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"the calculation\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"the next mark\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"buoy\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"the quickest time\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had not done a race yet and all these girls knew where the lay line was.\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"all these girls\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"the lay line\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These girls are amazing, Marta's an amazing friend and sailor and it could not have gone to a nicer person.\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These girls\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"Marta's an amazing friend\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"sailor\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"a nicer person\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really happy for her but I am just not sure I can keep putting myself through that format.\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that format\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just hope I can inspire some kids.\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some kids\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What I have done this week, I feel like I have shown that you can dominate a sport and if you show them that you can work hard and that's what happens, that's a win.\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"a win\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd love to go home with gold medal but I suppose bronze will have to do.\\\"\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold medal\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3393}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A World Sailing spokesman told the PA news agency: \\\"The decision was made following a recommendation by the World Sailing events committee, and voted on by the World Sailing council, which is comprised of elected officials from national sailing federations.\\\"\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3436, \"end\": 3449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Sailing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Sailing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Sailing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Sailing\"}, {\"begin\": 3542, \"end\": 3555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Sailing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wo